n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107</a><br />\n</span>樓主可唔可以pin? <img src=\"https://cdn.lihkg.com/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fmouse%2Fplease.gif&h=3d3ddc66&s={SIZE}\" />"}}